# Enforce LF line endings for source so gofmt stays consistent across OSes
# (Windows checkouts otherwise get CRLF via core.autocrlf and break gofmt -l).
* text=auto eol=lf
*.go text eol=lf
*.sql text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
Makefile text eol=lf

# Binary files: leave untouched
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.pdf binary
